changelogs.title: B11 Changelog
description: - Fixed crashes related to NPE (Keep hitting send crash report if you still get it)
- Fixed crashing bug when joining Hypixel
- Optifine capes now show (But Hyperium capes are still just as cool)
- Fixed an error with Spotify rendering
- Fixed the internal MC profiler always being on (Should improve performance)
- Added item to tab list to show if player is using Hyperium (Can be toggled in General Settings)
- Added /levelhead toggle to easily toggle Levelhead
- Added JPEG support to main menu background
